{
  "stem": "13395.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so the all the-- the privileges of a citizen of a country were slowly taken away from the German Jews, who were citizens of Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you, because I was too young at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I would not really know about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only things that I know is what was happening within the families and within Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how slowly-- for instance, my father had a school friend.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went to school together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were the same age.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was German-- so was my father, but he happened to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were very close friends, and they were visiting each other and spending-- they would come to our holidays to visit with us, and my parents would go for Christmas and visit with them and exchange gifts.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when 1933 the Nazis came to power, he was an engineer in the coal mine in Hindenburg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember that-- I was seven years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember when he came at night through the back door, knocked quietly on the door, and came in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he sat down with my father and said, it's very difficult to tell you what I came to tell you, but I had to join the Nazi party in order to stay-- keep my position in the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the-- the first prerequisite was that I have no Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He says, we will always be friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But we can't talk to each other any more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We can't see each other any more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was the first time that I realized that life is not going to be the same.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were so close.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
